@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #ECEFF1
skinparam classBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam classBorderColor #455A64
skinparam shadowing true
[*] --> Reviewed
Reviewed --> Processing : review
Processing --> OnHold : cancel
OnHold --> Rejected : reject
OnHold : entry / log catalog
Rejected --> Archived : approve
Archived --> Created : reject
Archived : entry / log catalog
Created --> [*]
@enduml